            . I live next door to the prosecutor. I saw the prisoner go up to the window, and take the watch off the table; he was taken immediately.</p>
               <p>JOHN HERBERT. I am surveyor of the Thames Police. I saw the prisoner running, and the prosecutor pursuing him; I collared him, he immediately took the watch out of his bosom, and gave it to him.</p>
